############################################################
# Solution
############################################################

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
Answers will vary, but the issue is that once you set the scale on both axes so that both [`(12,4)`] and [`(310,208)`] will appear, then [`(13,5)`] will appear to be so close to [`(12,4)`] that it will be challenging to draw them both and make it clear they are two different points.

